Bonang Matheba's reality show Being Bonang might have been glamorous and some of her followers may have even envied her fabulous lifestyle, which was often depicted on the show. While avid viewers of the reality show are still coming to terms with the fact  that it was her last season, the star has said "it was her worst working experience". In a shocking tweet, Queen B revealed that she didn't enjoy working on the third season of her show. .."making Being Bonang Season 3 was one of the worst working experiences of my life!! Glad it’s ending..... remind me to tell ya’ll why one day!", she tweeted. Her tweet proves once again that not all the glitters is gold.  